e":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2dc778aa94b4f3d369b75575df11db349cf83f","tid":1460272,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T02:57:12.000Z","msg":"好難去提防<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當有人做出勇武行為 咁點先知佢係真心定想嫁禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"有咩嫁禍，射核彈都唔割"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"I mean 隻鬼會令到政府夠證據去告暴動 雖然佢依家都係老屈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"暴動定義含糊，唔會因為你做咗某d 事先可以告得"},{"pid":"fc171146910c570d7d1ffcf5b5b1b9605f59ffd9","tid":1460272,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9fbe84591386b10d7c1ba7d2496a0cfe5d635441","tid":1460272,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T03:44:21.000Z","msg":"Pish,諗到再打"},{"pid":"eb316374e8b6cdceb02a16dc0c429b00fef90ad9","tid":1460272,"uid":274329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:02:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n1. 政府立刻正名撤回逃犯條例<br />\n2. 立刻成立以大法官為首的獨立調查委員會作全面調查<br />\n3. 收回暴動定性，停止白色恐佈，釋放所有政治犯，承諾不秋後算帳<br />\n4. 特首、律政司、保安局局長、警務處處長失職導致社會撕裂應問責下台<br />\n5. 在沒有831框架下重啟政改，盡快落實雙普選，以解決政府沒代表性，政策倒行逆施的問題</span>"},{"pid":"7a6a594ee0096bb97ff0ae45289904eb6bd67729","tid":1460272,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}